# Once done this will define
#
#  IDSUEYE_FOUND - system has IDS uEye SDK
#  IDSUEYE_INCLUDE_DIR - the IDS uEye SDK include directory
#  IDSUEYE_LIBRARIES - the libraries needed to use IDS uEye SDK

